  "description": "Aquatic Chain showcase emphasizing Fathom's maximum-depth character. OXBOW's entangled reverb already has internal density; Fathom at Character 0.0 (full dark/deep mode) adds multiband compression that further pushes energy into the low-mid body, creating a foundation-weight texture suitable for grounding a dense arrangement. Drift minimal (2 voices, 2ms depth) — this is about mass, not movement. Tide off. Reef at modest size 0.4 — OXBOW provides most of the reverb space already.",
